notes[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-06-02T05:23:36.705Z",codex,"Added native registerImporter('todos') + registerExporter('todos') pipeline (reusing shared runTodoImport/buildTodoMarkdown cores). Importer serves the pm todos import route and reads positional <file> arg + --glob/--section/--closed-as/--no-section-tags/--type/--priority/--tags. Parser now handles -/*/+ bullets, nested sub-tasks (indent preserved), ## section headers slugged to tags, and (p0-4)/!/!!/!!! priority markers stripped from titles. Functional: throwaway pm init+install, doctor active 0 failures, imported 7-item nested+sectioned TODO, round-trip export back to markdown verified. build+tsc+test all green."
close_reason: "Shipped: native todos importer/exporter pipeline + enhanced parser (nested sub-tasks, --glob multi-file, ## section->tags, (p1)/! priority) + --section/--closed-as/--glob/--no-section-tags flags. All verification passed (build, tsc --noEmit, test, functional round-trip)."
